name: Soontir_Fel
content:
Soontir Fel was a human Imperial Starfighter Pilot who became a Baron of the Empire and led the elite Imperial TIE Interceptor squadron Saber Squadron.
Soontir Fel was first mentioned in the Star Wars canon on a card titled "Saber Squadron Ace" in the Skystrike Academy Squadron Pack, a 2021 expansion for the miniatures game Star Wars: X-Wing Second Edition by Fantasy Flight Games. In the Star Wars Legends continuity, Soontir Fel first appeared in the twenty-first issue of the comic series Star Wars: X-Wing Rogue Squadron, written by Michael A. Stackpole, illustrated by John Nadeau, and published by Dark Horse Comics on August 6, 1997.
